text has been such an anchoring presence for me in the midst of a lot of tumultuous sort of uncertain, challenging, chaotic times at moments that we've had this fall together.

02:00.836 --> 02:05.925
One of my real go-to prayers for many years has been, the Lord is my shepherd.

02:07.007 --> 02:08.850
I lack nothing.

02:09.762 --> 02:18.955
When it seems like things are swirling out of control, when it feels like the future's uncertain, when I don't know that I feel like I'm adequate enough for the tax before me.

02:19.476 --> 02:21.278
