02:24.924 --> 02:26.165
The Lord is my shepherd.

02:27.207 --> 02:29.130
I lack nothing.

02:30.131 --> 02:33.095
And the reality of that song becomes true in my life.

02:33.155 --> 02:37.842
And I feel the Savior's and the shepherd's presence right here with me.

02:38.242 --> 02:41.446
