02:42.207 --> 02:52.058
People average marketing studies show that between five and 10,000 ads flash before our eyes every single day.

02:53.339 --> 03:06.354
If you only had this, if you only purchased that, if you only had that experience, if you weren't so old or weren't so young or whatever it is that causes you to be discontent, if you just bought this product then,

03:06.434 --> 03:08.096
