04:46.570 --> 04:57.266
People who are experiencing the sufficiency of the shepherd are those who are experiencing and receiving and sharing the very love of the shepherd.

04:57.506 --> 05:03.295
And so we're gonna look at four things today about how do we grow in love through the lens of Psalm 23.

05:03.335 --> 05:07.702
To really grow as Christ-like loving people.

05:08.924 --> 05:10.687
God is the one who initiates.

05:10.987 --> 05:14.593
God loves us and we need to learn to receive His love.

05:15.034 --> 05:16.837
Then secondly, we love God.

05:16.897 --> 05:20.322
Third, we love others.

05:20.543 --> 05:25.170
And then lastly, we become a community of Christ-like love.

05:25.474 --> 05:28.199
with very love of the shepherd is what permeates our lives.

05:28.259 --> 05:40.402
But I think the biggest obstacle that a lot of us have for growing in love and growing and being a loving community is a lot of us resist receiving the love of God.

05:41.410 --> 05:44.093
I don't know about you, but I struggle to receive gifts.

05:44.273 --> 05:47.116
My birthday's coming up soon and people ask, what do you want for your birthday?

05:47.136 --> 05:47.677
I'm like, I'm good.

05:47.697 --> 05:49.138
