07:13.342 --> 07:14.183
It's carried with me.

07:14.203 --> 07:27.421
And if you haven't memorized Psalm 23 yet in this series, I hope you'll spend time doing so because I lean on this Psalm and it helps me sense the Savior's presence so much throughout my ordinary everyday life.

07:28.002 --> 07:36.594
So as we hear it, let's pay attention to the shepherding love of God for you and for me and for us as well.

07:39.074 --> 07:40.716
The Lord is my shepherd.

07:41.937 --> 07:43.019
I lack nothing.

07:44.000 --> 07:46.703
He makes me lie down in green pastures.

07:47.324 --> 07:49.847
He leads me beside still waters.

07:50.567 --> 07:52.550
He restores my soul.

07:53.451 --> 07:57.816
He leads me on past of righteousness for his namesake.

07:58.777 --> 08:06.546
Even though I walk through the valley of the shadow of death, I will fear no evil for you are with me.

08:06.882 --> 08:09.505
your rod and your staff, they comfort me.

08:10.306 --> 08:14.130
