Now from our worldly standpoint, there are disappointments and things in life that ultimately happen, but in God's great, great plan.

11:16.738 --> 11:24.146
We will never be let down because of his faithful hassid that pursues us all the days of our lives.

11:24.610 --> 11:27.334
I'm a huge fan of the Jesus storybook Bible.

11:27.434 --> 11:30.959
