14:52.706 --> 14:55.550
And we just bury all of our emotions.

14:55.570 --> 15:01.617
The only time we express emotions was at a Steelers game, waving those annoying yellow, terrible towels, according to the rest of the world.

15:01.637 --> 15:02.358
