15:04.701 --> 15:11.168
And so I was in my 20s when this book came out, and Scazero actually came out to my school in Colorado where we went.

15:11.208 --> 15:15.954
And I had realized through his story that I have just

15:16.034 --> 15:23.905
buried so much of my emotions, and one of the ways I do that is by staying really, really busy for God.

